text: Fely Acuna (born 1936) is a Filipino actress who made films under LVN Pictures. Her first film in LVN was Pasikat opposite Carlos Salazar. == Filmography== * Pasikat (1955) * Pilipino Kostum, No Touch (1955) ==External links== * Category:1936 births Category:Living people Category:Filipino film actresses
title: Fely Acuna
